trans-unit.source: Represents a case-insensitive collection of key/value pairs that you use in various places in the routing framework, such as when you define the default values for a route or when you generate a URL that is based on a route.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta una raccolta di coppie chiave/valore senza distinzione tra maiuscole e minuscole usate in diversi punti del framework di routing, ad esempio quando si definiscono i valori predefiniti per una route o si genera un URL basato su una route.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteValueDictionary> class enables you to work with collections of key/value pairs that are required in order to use ASP.NET routing.
trans-unit.target: La <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteValueDictionary> classe consente di lavorare con le raccolte di coppie chiave/valore che sono necessari per il routing ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: You use the <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteValueDictionary> object to define values for the <xref:System.Web.Routing.Route.Constraints%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Routing.Route.DataTokens%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Routing.Route.Defaults%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Utilizzare il <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteValueDictionary> oggetto per definire i valori per il <xref:System.Web.Routing.Route.Constraints%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Routing.Route.DataTokens%2A>, e <xref:System.Web.Routing.Route.Defaults%2A> proprietà.

trans-unit.source: You also use a <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteValueDictionary> object when you generate a URL by calling the <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteCollection.GetVirtualPath%2A> method and passing a <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteValueDictionary> object as a parameter.
trans-unit.target: È inoltre possibile utilizzare un <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteValueDictionary> oggetto quando si genera un URL chiamando il <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteCollection.GetVirtualPath%2A> metodo e passando un <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteValueDictionary> oggetto come parametro.

trans-unit.source: Every key in a <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteValueDictionary> object must be unique.
trans-unit.target: Ogni chiave in un <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteValueDictionary> l'oggetto deve essere univoco.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteValueDictionary> class uses case-insensitive ordinal comparison.
trans-unit.target: La <xref:System.Web.Routing.RouteValueDictionary> classe utilizza il confronto ordinale tra maiuscole e minuscole.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.StringComparer.OrdinalIgnoreCase%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Per ulteriori informazioni, vedere <xref:System.StringComparer.OrdinalIgnoreCase%2A>.

trans-unit.source: A key cannot be `null`.
trans-unit.target: Non può essere una chiave `null`.
